Kaizer Chiefs legend Ntsie Maphike has compared his son with a tough boxer who can take punishment from opponents. Maphike, who used to add stability in Amakhosi defence with a knack for goals in the heydays made this statement via Twitter after his son made him proud by passing matric. Said Maphike: "Like father like son. Well done my boy, it was not easy, you were like a good boxer that can take punishment, I hope matric is not the end."